e.org/fhir/space-health/CodeSystem/nasa-medical-hardware-cs#12-lead-ecg (\"12-Lead ECG Machine\")</li><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">https://mitre.org/fhir/space-health/CodeSystem/nasa-medical-hardware-cs#blood-pressure-monitor (\"Blood Pressure Monitor\")</li><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">https://mitre.org/fhir/space-health/CodeSystem/nasa-medical-hardware-cs#dexa (\"DEXA Scanner\")</li><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">https://mitre.org/fhir/space-health/CodeSystem/nasa-medical-hardware-cs#audiometer (\"Audiometer\")</li><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">Ultrasound</li><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">Defibrillator</li><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">Pulse Oximeter</li></ul><a name=\"opt-item.calibration.status\"> </a><p><b>Answer options for calibration.status </b></p><ul><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">Current</li><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">Due Soon (within 30 days)</li><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">Overdue</li><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">Not Applicable</li></ul><a name=\"opt-item.preventive-maintenance.tasks-completed\"> </a><p><b>Answer options for preventive-maintenance.tasks-completed </b></p><ul><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">Visual inspection</li><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">Cleaning</li><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">Battery check/replacement</li><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">Consumables replacement</li><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">Functional verification</li><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">Software update</li></ul><a name=\"opt-item.functionality-status.condition\"> </a><p><b>Answer options for functionality-status.condition </b></p><ul><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">Excellent</li><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">Good</li><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">Fair - Minor issues</li><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">Poor - Needs repair</li><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">Non-functional</li></ul><a name=\"opt-item.data-delivery.archive\"> </a><p><b>Answer options for data-delivery.archive </b></p><ul><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">https://mitre.org/fhir/space-health/CodeSystem/nasa-data